# Optio Platform - Environment Variables
#
# Backend config: see backend/.env.example (authoritative reference)
# Frontend config: see frontend/.env.example
#
# Quick setup:
#   cp backend/.env.example backend/.env   # then fill in values
#   cp frontend/.env.example frontend/.env # then fill in values
#
# Generate a secure secret key:
#   python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"
#
# Security: Never commit .env files to git. They are gitignored.
